  <h1>About SnippetBox</h1>

  <p>
    SnippetBox is a simple tool for sharing code snippets and files. 
    Perfect for teachers sharing materials with students or developers 
    sharing code examples.
  </p>

  <h2>How it works</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Create a share with markdown content and/or files</li>
    <li>Get a short URL to share with others</li>
    <li>Edit your share for 30 days (if you have the edit cookie)</li>
    <li><strong>All shares automatically expire after 30 days</strong></li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Features</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Markdown support with syntax highlighting</li>
    <li>Upload up to 5 files (5MB each)</li>
    <li>Custom URLs</li>
    <li>No account required</li>
  </ul>

